schools.name: Dr. Martin Luther King, Jr. Early College

data.description:
Imagine waking up every day in a nearly-new house, located in a the prime Green Valley Ranch area. Upgraded with granite counters, top-tier cabinets in a bright, open and flooded with natural light. The upstairs features two good-sized bedrooms, a primary ensuite bathroom and a roomy loft. Photos have been virtually staged to show design possibilities in your new home.

Outside, a beautifully landscaped yard features a custom pergola - a great spot to relax. The location is a gem - within walking distance, you'll find a golf course, shopping options like King Soopers, Sprouts and Costco and parks.

Picture your day: waking up to sunlight streaming in. A quick walk to the Corner Bakery for brunch. Maybe a round of golf. Everything you need is close by. With close proximity to the Denver International Airport and nearby Gaylord Rockies Resort, you're in the perfect place for family and friends to visit. 

Don't miss out - your dream home is waiting!
